{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_pGHiEZl0tmvvckUFZB3MCLO7","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Desktop Goose samperson itch.io download features description\"\n\nSearch results for query:\n\nNo links found.\n\nI don't have access to a live web search tool in this environment, so I can't browse the current itch.io page in real-time. However, I can provide you with detailed information about **Desktop Goose** by **Samperson** (Sam Chiet) based on available knowledge:\n\n## Desktop Goose - Overview\n\n**Developer:** Samperson (Sam Chiet)  \n**Platform:** itch.io (Windows & macOS)  \n**Price:** Free / Pay-what-you-want  \n**Genre:** Desktop pet / Mischief simulator / Meme software\n\n## Key Features\n\n- **Mischievous Goose NPC:** A small goose that wanders around your desktop screen and interacts with your workflow\n- **Honking:** The goose makes honking sounds at random intervals\n- **Steals Your Cursor:** The goose will occasionally grab your mouse cursor and run away with it\n- **Drag Memes/Notes:** Brings images (memes) and text notes onto your screen from a folder you can customize\n- **Mud Tracks:** Leaves muddy footprints across your desktop that fade over time\n- **Attack Mode:** If you try to interact with it, the goose may \"attack\" (playfully) and drag windows around\n- **Customizable Content:** You can add your own images and notes to the Assets folder for the goose to bring onto screen\n- **Settings:** Adjustable aggression levels, sound controls, and content toggles\n\n## Download & Installation\n\n- Available directly from **samperson.itch.io/desktop-goose**\n- Download the ZIP file for your OS (Windows or macOS)\n- Extract and run the executable\n- No installation wizard required (portable application)\n\n## System Requirements\n\n- Lightweight application\n- Runs on most modern Windows and macOS systems\n- Minimal CPU/RAM usage\n\nIf you need the **exact current download link**, latest version number, or recent update notes, I'd recommend visiting `samperson.itch.io/desktop-goose` directly, as the page may have updates or patches newer than my knowledge cutoff.\n\nWould you like help with anything specific about installing or customizing the goose?\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"36ea181f-816c-4d44-9503-0b29dcdbf90f","uuid":"308f2e7f-dd01-41ed-8544-6f8df5b6e23a","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:06:44.122Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Desktop Goose samperson itch.io download features description","results":["Search results for query:",{"content":[]},"I don't have access to a live web search tool in this environment, so I can't browse the current itch.io page in real-time. However, I can provide you with detailed information about **Desktop Goose** by **Samperson** (Sam Chiet) based on available knowledge:\n\n## Desktop Goose - Overview\n\n**Developer:** Samperson (Sam Chiet)  \n**Platform:** itch.io (Windows & macOS)  \n**Price:** Free / Pay-what-you-want  \n**Genre:** Desktop pet / Mischief simulator / Meme software\n\n## Key Features\n\n- **Mischievous Goose NPC:** A small goose that wanders around your desktop screen and interacts with your workflow\n- **Honking:** The goose makes honking sounds at random intervals\n- **Steals Your Cursor:** The goose will occasionally grab your mouse cursor and run away with it\n- **Drag Memes/Notes:** Brings images (memes) and text notes onto your screen from a folder you can customize\n- **Mud Tracks:** Leaves muddy footprints across your desktop that fade over time\n- **Attack Mode:** If you try to interact with it, the goose may \"attack\" (playfully) and drag windows around\n- **Customizable Content:** You can add your own images and notes to the Assets folder for the goose to bring onto screen\n- **Settings:** Adjustable aggression levels, sound controls, and content toggles\n\n## Download & Installation\n\n- Available directly from **samperson.itch.io/desktop-goose**\n- Download the ZIP file for your OS (Windows or macOS)\n- Extract and run the executable\n- No installation wizard required (portable application)\n\n## System Requirements\n\n- Lightweight application\n- Runs on most modern Windows and macOS systems\n- Minimal CPU/RAM usage\n\nIf you need the **exact current download link**, latest version number, or recent update notes, I'd recommend visiting `samperson.itch.io/desktop-goose` directly, as the page may have updates or patches newer than my knowledge cutoff.\n\nWould you like help with anything specific about installing or customizing the goose?"],"durationSeconds":20.243147665999945,"searchCount":1}}
