{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_PbJ2OjUwzkLfwTeywBSBrspz","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Desktop Goose by Samperson itch.io download features description\"\n\nSearch results for query:\n\nNo links found.\n\nI don't have the ability to perform live web searches in this environment, but I can provide you with information about **Desktop Goose** by **Samperson** (Sam Chiet) based on my existing knowledge:\n\n## Overview\n**Desktop Goose** is a popular desktop pet application created by **Samperson** and distributed primarily through **itch.io**. It was released in 2020 and became a viral sensation. Unlike traditional cute desktop pets, the goose is intentionally chaotic and mildly annoying.\n\n## Download & Availability\n- **Platform:** Available on **itch.io** (itch.io/samperson/desktop-goose)\n- **Price:** Originally pay-what-you-want (with a minimum of free/$0)\n- **Platforms:** Windows and macOS versions available\n- **File size:** Relatively small, lightweight application\n\n## Key Features & Description\n- **Desktop Companion:** A small goose that walks around your screen and interacts with your workspace\n- **Honking:** The goose frequently honks, both audibly and visually\n- **Note/Meme System:** It can drag memes, images, and text notes onto your screen from a customizable folder\n- **Mud Tracking:** The goose leaves muddy footprints across your desktop that fade over time\n- **Chasing the Cursor:** It sometimes chases or steals your mouse cursor\n- **Window Interaction:** The goose can grab and drag windows around your screen\n- **Untamed Behavior:** You cannot fully control the goose—it operates autonomously and disrupts your workflow intentionally\n- **Customizable Content:** Users can add their own images/memes to the goose's inventory folder\n- **Settings:** Options to adjust aggression level, meme frequency, and other behaviors\n\n## Concept\nDesktop Goose is essentially a love-letter to/parody of classic desktop assistants (like Clippy or virtual pets), designed to be a chaotic but charming distraction while you work.\n\nWould you like me to help you find the specific itch.io page URL, or do you have questions about installing or customizing the goose?\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"36ea181f-816c-4d44-9503-0b29dcdbf90f","uuid":"6a1a92b6-2237-4703-87ab-88762916e6d2","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:09:44.637Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Desktop Goose by Samperson itch.io download features description","results":["Search results for query:",{"content":[]},"I don't have the ability to perform live web searches in this environment, but I can provide you with information about **Desktop Goose** by **Samperson** (Sam Chiet) based on my existing knowledge:\n\n## Overview\n**Desktop Goose** is a popular desktop pet application created by **Samperson** and distributed primarily through **itch.io**. It was released in 2020 and became a viral sensation. Unlike traditional cute desktop pets, the goose is intentionally chaotic and mildly annoying.\n\n## Download & Availability\n- **Platform:** Available on **itch.io** (itch.io/samperson/desktop-goose)\n- **Price:** Originally pay-what-you-want (with a minimum of free/$0)\n- **Platforms:** Windows and macOS versions available\n- **File size:** Relatively small, lightweight application\n\n## Key Features & Description\n- **Desktop Companion:** A small goose that walks around your screen and interacts with your workspace\n- **Honking:** The goose frequently honks, both audibly and visually\n- **Note/Meme System:** It can drag memes, images, and text notes onto your screen from a customizable folder\n- **Mud Tracking:** The goose leaves muddy footprints across your desktop that fade over time\n- **Chasing the Cursor:** It sometimes chases or steals your mouse cursor\n- **Window Interaction:** The goose can grab and drag windows around your screen\n- **Untamed Behavior:** You cannot fully control the goose—it operates autonomously and disrupts your workflow intentionally\n- **Customizable Content:** Users can add their own images/memes to the goose's inventory folder\n- **Settings:** Options to adjust aggression level, meme frequency, and other behaviors\n\n## Concept\nDesktop Goose is essentially a love-letter to/parody of classic desktop assistants (like Clippy or virtual pets), designed to be a chaotic but charming distraction while you work.\n\nWould you like me to help you find the specific itch.io page URL, or do you have questions about installing or customizing the goose?"],"durationSeconds":16.864814459000016,"searchCount":1}}
